      <title>英国福利改革将有25万人陷入贫困</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/uk-welfare-reforms-to-drive-250k-more-people-into-poverty</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据政府对政府对政府叛乱的政策的评估，到2030年，一百万人中有四分之一的人将到2030年将到2030年将在英国陷入相对贫困。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/uk-welfare-reforms-to-drive-250k-more-people-into-poverty</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Mar 2025 15:14:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Gabbard说，随着聊天文本的发布，没有共享任何分类信息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/gabbard-says-no-classified-info-shared-as-chat-texts-published</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国家情报局主管塔尔西·加巴德（Tulsi Gabbard）重申，在美国官员之间的聊天中，没有分享任何机密信息，该官员无意中的军事行动将包括一名记者在内。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/gabbard-says-no-classified-info-shared-as-chat-texts-published</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Mar 2025 14:51:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>最高法院坚持我们对“幽灵枪”套件的监管</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/supreme-court-upholds-us-regulation-of-ghost-gun-kits</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国最高法院维持了联邦内置的“幽灵枪”套件的法规，支持在拜登政府期间制定的一项规则，以阻止官员们说的是不可追踪的武器的洪流。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/supreme-court-upholds-us-regulation-of-ghost-gun-kits</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Mar 2025 14:09:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>卡尼在贸易战中承诺为加拿大汽车行业数十亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/carney-pledges-billions-for-canadian-auto-sector-in-trade-war</link>
      <description><![CDATA[自由党的领导人马克·卡尼（Mark Carney）承诺将有20亿加元（14亿美元）的“战略响应基金”，以帮助加拿大汽车制造业，并加强受到美国关税威胁的供应链。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/carney-pledges-billions-for-canadian-auto-sector-in-trade-war</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Mar 2025 13:53:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>苏丹军队说，首都的中心从民兵中夺回</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/sudanese-army-says-capital-s-airport-recaptured-from-militia</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一名官员说，苏丹的陆军夺回了包括国际机场在内的中央喀土穆，越来越接近将迅速支持部队从首都路由路线，这将是两年的内战的转折点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/sudanese-army-says-capital-s-airport-recaptured-from-militia</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Mar 2025 11:30:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>万斯加入了格陵兰巡回演唱会，正如特朗普所说的“我们需要的”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/vances-new-greenland-travel-plans-offer-relief-for-denmark</link>
      <description><![CDATA[首先是唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump Jr）宣布，他的父亲说美国将吞并世界上最大的岛屿之后，他几周后“热火”到格陵兰。现在，副总统JD Vance正在那里参加旅行，因为他不希望他的妻子“独自获得所有乐趣”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/vances-new-greenland-travel-plans-offer-relief-for-denmark</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Mar 2025 09:07:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普在数周而不是几个月内权衡铜进口关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/trump-may-implement-copper-import-tariffs-within-weeks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据熟悉此事的人们说，美国对铜进口的关税可能会在几周内，比判决的截止日期提前几个月。在纽约交易的铜升至纪录。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/trump-may-implement-copper-import-tariffs-within-weeks</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Mar 2025 01:06:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普内阁官员在泄漏的信号聊天面对诉讼中</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/trump-cabinet-officials-in-group-chat-flap-face-a-lawsuit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统内阁的五名成员在诉讼中被指控违反了美国法律，该法律旨在通过使用加密的消息传递平台信号来保护政府记录，以沟通有关正式业务的法律。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/trump-cabinet-officials-in-group-chat-flap-face-a-lawsuit</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Mar 2025 00:12:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>纽约要求特朗普尽管威胁要收取过境资金，但仍要求更多的MTA援助</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/ny-asks-trump-for-more-mta-aid-amid-threat-to-pull-transit-funds</link>
      <description><![CDATA[纽约官员呼吁联邦政府向纽约市的公共交通系统提供更多援助，即使特朗普政府加强了其退缩资金的威胁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/ny-asks-trump-for-more-mta-aid-amid-threat-to-pull-transit-funds</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Mar 2025 21:07:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普司法敌人是卡瓦诺的室友，得到共和党的支持</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/trump-s-judicial-foe-was-kavanaugh-s-roommate-had-gop-s-backing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普总统说，法官是“激进的左疯子”，应该受到弹each。总检察长说他正在保护恐怖分子。司法部的律师说，他的裁决正在破坏委内瑞拉帮派成员的重要努力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/trump-s-judicial-foe-was-kavanaugh-s-roommate-had-gop-s-backing</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Mar 2025 15:16:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
